

Install open source licensing in all .c and .h files in directory tree.
Original files are renamed with .bak extension.  Existing .bak files (if any)
are silently over-written. Due caution is recommended.

USAGE: InstallLicense directory license year name email [options]
 license - PD, MIT or AGPL
 year    - copyright year[s]. use single quotes if necessary
 name    - copyright holder[s]. use single quotes if necessary
Options
 -p xxx  - program name and description, used by some licenses
 -d      - debug

